highlights.text: Turisti has the most spots on Top Songs Finland. “MEININKI” is the highest at #16.
“Ai Että” by Isac Elliot is the highest new entry on Top Songs Finland at #1.
“Viimeinen tanssi” by Behm and Olavi Uusivirta has been on Top Songs Finland the longest, at 120 weeks straight.
